room_title: Escape room "Night at the Museum" by Amazing Escape Room Cherry Hill in Collingswood
room_address: 2050 Springdale Rd Suite 200 Cherry Hill, NJ 08003
room_description: The Star Diamond Broach is a rare and priceless item on display for a limited time at the Art Museum of Cherry Hill. You and your band of thieves have to sneak in and get the diamond before the security system comes back on and the security guard returns. This is a time-sensitive mission, you only have 60 minutes to get in, get the diamond and get out. We are relying on you, please hurry and be careful.
